title: Gundlach: Considering taking off short on Chipotle
text:
Jeffrey Gundlach at Delivering Alpha 2015 in New York. 
This is breaking news. Please check back for updates. 
"Bond king" Jeffrey Gundlach said on Wednesday that he might take of his short on Chipotle stock, "because it is starting to perform well again." 
Speaking at CNBC's annual Delivering Alpha Conference in New York, Gundlach also said that he is considering a similar move for Delta Air Lines . 
Chipotle shares edged higher in midday trading, while Delta was trading slightly lower. 
Click here for more on Delivering Alpha.
